{"tid":1883113,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[黃店聯黃色youtube圈] 建議黃店依期可以拍埋片介紹鋪頭","createTime":"2020-02-16T17:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T20:15:02.000Z","uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0088537b5eff8d7675016c972849df5d60e73dc2","tid":1883113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎搞到大家少出街<br />\n學生哥又食唔到黃店<br />\n對黃店係好受打擊<br />\n不如順住黃色youtube圈個勢<br />\n各黃店主動自己拍片介紹下自己鋪頭<br />\n加入埋黃色youtube圈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（當然手足都可以去幫手拍）<br />\n之後搞黃店時，都有唔少「明星黃店」出現，其實黃店係有名氣同影響力，有人會注意同吹捧，只要加入一啲唔同元素嘅片種，其實係可以造到星<br />\n雖然拍片嘅要求、剪片、人手、成本同本身黃店可能好大差別，但係都可以嘗試下，喺鋪頭做下街訪、玩下遊戲，簡簡單單其實都係好好嘅軟性宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開完channel再可以搵人整合各區黃店同youtuber，加強地區嘅聯繫，又可以同區議員crossover講政治、時事、地區問題，其實好多嘢可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家足不出戶，其實都可以加強到社區聯繫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（仲可能可以賺到少少錢）"},{"pid":"03e117497bcfc566c2c844f92c97c107944fc0dc","tid":1883113,"uid":5103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:10:24.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土Youtube Channel？</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867920\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867920</a>"},{"pid":"1b8ef0d016f8232ab9327efa855eca27520a058e","tid":1883113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a63c9eaa7183463e7760e6bcafd50348f54b5e1","tid":1883113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898a899328796f15801d889e06534379c79065c3","tid":1883113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f642d71ab9f53b63db1f6cb4eb8cb022e198452b","tid":1883113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899a9324cfb08bac57e1cd373b834872a3797d6c","tid":1883113,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df3b7f6165482f7d2fd220fbbb6324e272c13d1","tid":1883113,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mater